name: aws-parallelcluster
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "aws-parallelcluster" %}
{% set version = "2.11.9" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 615de4d59d9fd56a31d4feb3aeefe685346538a8dd0c1c35b660029f891d4dfd

build:
  number: 2
  entry_points:
    - pcluster = pcluster.cli:main
    - awsbqueues = awsbatch.awsbqueues:main
    - awsbhosts = awsbatch.awsbhosts:main
    - awsbstat = awsbatch.awsbstat:main
    - awsbkill = awsbatch.awsbkill:main
    - awsbsub = awsbatch.awsbsub:main
    - awsbout = awsbatch.awsbout:main
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv '

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - boto3 >=1.16.14
    - tabulate >=0.8.8,<=0.8.10
    - future >=0.18.2
    - pyyaml >=5.3.1
    - configparser >=4.0.2  # [py2k]
    - jinja2 >=2.11.0

test:
  imports:
    - awsbatch
    - pcluster
  commands:
    - pcluster --help
    - awsbqueues --help
    - awsbhosts --help
    - awsbstat --help
    - awsbkill --help
    - awsbsub --help
    - awsbout --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/aws/aws-parallelcluster
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: {{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.txt
  summary: AWS ParallelCluster is an AWS supported Open Source cluster management tool to deploy and manage HPC clusters in the AWS cloud.
  doc_url: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/parallelcluster
  dev_url: https://github.com/aws/aws-parallelcluster

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - notestaff
    - sean-smith
    - lukeseawalker
    - demartinofra
    - enrico-usai
    - chenwany
    - charlesg3
    - hanwen-pcluste
    - gmarciani
    - francesco-giordano
